{"word":"νομικός","slug":"νομικός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>νομιϰός, ή, όν</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νόμος\">νόμος</a></el>] ‘having to do with law’, as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a> <b>about law <a href='B:630 3:9'>Tit 3:9</a>;</b> as noun <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νομικός\">νομικός</a></el> <b>legal expert, lawyer,</b> of experts in Mosaic law <b><a href='B:470 22:35'>Mt 22:35</a>; <a href='B:490 7:30'>Lk 7:30</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> The legal specialty of one named Zenas cannot be determined <b><a href='B:630 3:13'>Tit 3:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:νομίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:νομίμως\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}